comments: White (SAS) engages with Harris (PHI) on his pick, but he quickly disengages as Harris rolls into a post up.
Embiid (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by DeRozan (SAS).
Gay (SAS) wraps Horford (PHI) and the contact affects his FOM.
Harris (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Murray's (SAS) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Poeltl (SAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Richardson's (PHI) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Embiid (PHI) has a forearm to Poeltl's (SAS) back in the post, but he does not extend or deliver contact that dislodges him from his legal guarding position.
Embiid (PHI) makes marginal contact to Poeltl's (SAS) shoulder as he turns and passes the ball to Harris (PHI).

As Milton (PHI) disengages from the pick, he briefly grasps Poeltl's (SAS) shorts as he slides his hand off his hip to a resting position on his back.  The contact does not affect Poeltl's SQBR on his roll to the rim.
Poeltl (SAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Milton's (PHI) path and absorbs the contact.
Embiid (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Murray (SAS).
As they both jump for the ball, Embiid (PHI) makes incidental contact to Poeltl's (SAS) body during the rebound.
Harris (PHI) makes marginal contact to Poeltl's (SAS) back during the rebound and the contact doesn't affect his ability to retrieve the ball.
Poeltl (SAS) makes contact to Embiid's (PHI) arm in the post.
Harris (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position on Poeltl (SAS) and makes clean ball contact on his steal attempt before the timeout is whistled.
Embiid (PHI) and Gay (SAS) engage and separate during the inbound.
Thybulle (PHI) engages with Mills (SAS) during the inbound and as they separate they make incidental leg to leg contact.
Harris (PHI) makes contact to Murray's (SAS) arm and the illegal contact dislodges the ball into the backcourt.
During the inbound, Embiid (PHI) and Poeltl (SAS) make marginal contact with one another in the post as they compete for position.
Harris (PHI) commits a take foul on White (SAS).
Gay (SAS) and Horford (PHI) engage and disengage during the inbound.
While the shot is in the air, Poeltl (SAS) makes incidental foot to foot contact with his teammate DeRozan (SAS) that causes him to stumble.
Richardson (PHI) engages with DeRozan (SAS) during the inbound and DeRozan makes marginal contact to Richardson's back as he attempts to disengage.
Harris (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact during the play at the basket by Poeltl (SAS).
Replay Review of the out of bounds gets overturned and Philadelphia is given possession.
Poeltl (SAS) commits a take foul on Embiid (PHI).
